To our BookExpo, UnBound and BookCon community— After many hours of conversation, we have decided to postpone BookExpo, UnBound and BookCon from May to July 22-26 at the Javits Center. Our hearts go out to our entire community and every individual person and business impacted by the COVID-19 virus. Please read a message from our Event Director, Jenny Martin: https://bit.ly/3dgVrMv
